{
  "stem": "11671.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you, you asked if we worked.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only thing occ-- occasionally my sister was picked to work with-- the work consisted of chopping stones.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We could never figure out what it was, but she would just go for that one day and chop stones and then come back.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then the only-- the work that we participated in was that they asked for volunteers to carry the food from the kitchen to the barracks.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we got our porridge and piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had these huge milk cans that two people had to go in the kitchen and get it and either the grass soup that we got or the porridge and to carry it to the barracks, and then help dish it out.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we always volunteered to do that chore because people were very weak, and people were lethargic and didn't want to, really didn't care what was happening anymore.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so we, we felt that we-- by doing a little work and volunteering and keeping active, it will help us survive.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that was the only choice we did there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We, we, we lost-- as soon as we arrived, I mean, because of the lack of food, the next month none of us women menstruated.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That quickly, one month later.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I always felt that it could not have been caused by just a lack of food and starvation in one month.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I always felt that perhaps something was put in our food because everyone, every one of us stopped menstruating as soon as we arrived in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were weak and cold.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was more religious than my sisters.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I refused to eat the food.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
